
Marketing and Launch

    Pre-Launch:
        Build a landing page to capture early interest and emails.
        Use social media to generate buzz with teaser videos and behind-the-scenes content.

    Launch:
        Run a targeted ad campaign on social media and Google Ads.
        Partner with travel bloggers and influencers to promote the app.

    Post-Launch:
        Regularly update the app with new content and features.
        Gather user feedback and iterate on the app to improve the user experience.


Analytics and User Feedback

    User Analytics:
        Track user engagement, popular tours, session duration, and more using tools like Google Analytics for Firebase.

    Feedback Mechanism:
        Provide an easy way for users to give feedback and report issues within the app.

    Continuous Improvement:
        Use data and feedback to continuously improve content and features.
